relation: A model of a Mr. Saturn I made using modeling clay. Made by BackintheDayEB (Scott Sparr).
I gave my old SNES an Earthbound facelift. Now my Earthbound Cartridge feels more at home.
I used four different medias for this picture of Ness. colored pen, pencil, marker and MS Paint.
(Note: Sorry, here is a Jpeg version.) Made by Scott Sparr (BackInTheDayEB). This is a depiction of the ostentatious serenity of Winters. Enjoy.
A depiction of Robotic Ness alone in the Cave of the Past. Artist: BackintheDayEB Scott A. Sparr
